values:
I was driving to the resturant today.

tell me, why is it always nasty when I go into work, then clears up with an hour to go then gets nasty again.

I just don't trust this weather.  In fact, I have a hard time trusting many things.

But I was driving to work, smoking, and minding my own business, when I see flashing blue lights in the distance, and my heart dropped.
